(3) A school administrator must complete the orientation and training
developed by the department pursuant to subdivision (a)(1) prior to conducting a
search pursuant to § 49-6-4204(a)(2)(C) or § 49-6-4205(a)(2)(C).
SECTION 6. Section 5 of this act takes effect upon becoming a law, the public welfare
requiring it. All other sections of this act take effect July 1, 2025, the public welfare requiring it.
